\f2 \uc0\u9642 
\f0 	}You may have no desire to feed an alligator but if you live in Florida - the people down there are very comfortable with them...in fact too comfortable\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Disney death\
