\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u9642 
\f0 	}These stories are tragic and many preventable\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u9642 
\f0 	}And it would be easy to think you would never do something so crazy...but you do...we all do.\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u9642 
\f0 	}If you haven't figured it out yet...this book really isn't about alligators and how to care for them.\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u9642 
\f0 	}It's about you...it's about me...and our desire to feed and become comfortable around the very things that will be our own destruction\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u9642 
\f0 	}Examples\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
