\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Ecc 10:1-2 - small sin will kill great character\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}2 Sam 11 - It all starts with a small compromise...and it wasn't even a 'sin'...but it was an alligator.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li2160\fi-2160\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}That's the problem with alligators...if you keep looking through the scripture for a loophole on your issue then you'll for sure find it...there is no way you can catch them all (Pokemon Go)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}And don't miss that his sin of sloth (staying home and not working) led to others seemingly unconnected sins\
\pard\tx2380\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li2880\fi-2880\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl3\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Lust, Wrath, Envy, Pride, etc... (maybe all of them)\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\tx2240\tx2800\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li2160\fi-2160\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Go backwards and trick them into thinking it was him looking at the woman who was not his wife that was the problem...but it was an even small alligator than that...it's laziness or slothfulness. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}I'm sure David justified and rationalized his compromise...and the saddest part is David may never have connected that one small decision to stay home with the chaos, sin, and lives ruined that followed. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}But we have the benefit of the authors perspective...to see the whole picture.\
