\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}The most cautious person in the world...the most scared cautious person in the world who doesn't understand how anyone could play around even near an alligator...has them swimming all around them 24/7...we just don't call them alligators...we call them small sins or compromises\
